  <thing id="fDilet" name="Dilettante" description="{i}What some would call dabbling you call a wide range of interests. Your breath of knowledge offers unexpected insights in many situations.{/i}\n\n{b}Prerequisites:{/b} 2 ranks each in 5 different Knowledge skills.\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} You gain a +2 bonus on Knowledge checks if you have 1-5 ranks in that skill. This bonus does not stack with Skill Focus. You can make untrained Knowledge checks with DC&apos;s up to 15.\n\n{/b}Normal:{/b} You may only make untrained Knolwedge checks for common knowledge (DC 10 or lower)." compset="Feat" summary="You have a wide range of interests and knowledge which offers insights in many situations.">
    <comment>EDITOR NOTE: Does not affect skills.</comment>
    <fieldval field="shortname" value="Dilettante"/>
    <usesource source="PFSkrSecrt"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="ShowSpec"/>
    </thing>
  <thing id="fFrndSwt" name="Friendly Switch" description="{i}You elbow an ally out of the way, and take his palce on the battlefield.{/I}\n\n{b}Prerequisites:{/b} Base Attack Bonus +1\n\n{b}Benefit:{/b} As part of your movement or as a 5-foot-step, you can move into the space occupied by an ally of your size or smaller, which displaces the ally into the space you just left. Your ally must be willing and able to move and to occupy the space you were in. This movement does not provoke attacks of opportunity. This does not count toward your ally&apos;s movement on this next turn." compset="Feat" summary="You elbow an ally out of the way, and take his palce on the battlefield." uniqueness="useronce">
